data.description: Lots of home for the money.  This older 2-story has some updates, character, good bones and you can finish it up as you please.  Plenty of space and a functional basement/workshop area for your tools and hobbies.  It's easy to see and you get possession at close.  Hurry; you can be in by Christmas.
